Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteReportingIDS

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteReportingIDS
public class JDBWasteReportingIDS extends Object
The JDBWasteReportingIDS class updates the table APP_WASTE_REPORTING_IDS. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Transaction Type as stored in the APP_WASTE_REPORTING_IDS table.
